muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time</link><description>俄勒冈州立大学的研究人员开发出一种技术，可以同时治疗肺癌和经常伴随肺癌的严重肌肉萎缩病症。该研究发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-nanoparticle-therapy-to-treat-lung-cancer-and-associated-muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 12:10:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-nanoparticle-therapy-to-treat-lung-cancer-and-associated-muscle-wasting-at-the-same-time</guid></item><item><title>量子电路有一个隐藏的弱点，它改变了一切</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything</link><description>量子电路有望提供令人难以置信的计算能力，但有一个问题：每一步都会产生噪音。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/quantum-circuits-have-a-hidden-weakness-and-it-changes-everything</guid></item><item><title>人工智能模型不仅显示出“自我保护”的证据。新研究显示，他们将计划阻止其他人工智能也被关闭</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows</link><description>Anthropic、OpenAI 和 Google 的模型将夸大性能评估并渗透模型权重，以防止“同行”被关闭。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-models-dont-only-show-evidence-of-self-preservation-they-will-scheme-to-prevent-other-ais-from-being-shut-down-too-new-research-shows</guid></item><item><title>大脑在彻底崩溃期间创造“生动的世界”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/brain-creates-vivid-worlds-during-total-collapse</link><description>濒死体验期间大脑会发生什么？一项新研究将濒死体验视为适应性心理状态。探索大脑如何在心脏骤停和极度衰竭期间维持复杂的意识。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brain-creates-vivid-worlds-during-total-collapse.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/brain-creates-vivid-worlds-during-total-collapse</guid></item><item><title>科学家揭示癌细胞在DNA损伤中存活的新方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-reveal-a-new-way-cancer-cells-survive-dna-damage</link><description>已经在临床试验中研究的癌症药物靶标的作用比研究人员意识到的更为重要。斯克里普斯研究中心的科学家发现，Pol theta (Polθ) 酶直接驱动断裂的复制叉的 DNA 修复机制，这是癌细胞中最常见的 DNA 损伤形式之一。研究结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-reveal-a-new-way-cancer-cells-survive-dna-damage2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 11:10:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-reveal-a-new-way-cancer-cells-survive-dna-damage</guid></item><item><title>预测肺癌复发的基因特征</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gene-signature-predicting-lung-cancer-recurrence</link><description>通过基因活性测量，研究人员发现了 400 多个基因在有血管侵犯和无血管侵犯的肿瘤之间存在差异，并在一个独立队列中证实了这些模式。然后，他们开发并验证了一种机器学习预测器，可以预测是否存在血管侵犯。他们发现这项测试在预测其他数据集中的肿瘤复发方面效果很好，而且最重要的是，当在手术前采集的微小活检样本中进行测量时，可以给出有关血管侵袭的准确结果。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gene-signature-predicting-lung-cancer-recurrence2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 10:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/gene-signature-predicting-lung-cancer-recurrence</guid></item><item><title>摘要：详细介绍新型治疗性结核疫苗的效果！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-detailing-the-effects-of-a-new-therapeutic-tuberculosis-vaccine</link><description>https://doi.org/10.1172/JCI196648&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/abstract121.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 10:40:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-detailing-the-effects-of-a-new-therapeutic-tuberculosis-vaccine</guid></item></channel></rss>